Audit & Controlling Officer
Orient Electronics (Pvt) LTD
-
Lahore
Job Description:
Routine Examination and Analysis of Management Accounting system.
Financial Statements Analysis and reporting.
Profitability Analysis.
Profit Centers and Cost Centers reporting
Review, analyze implement the comprehensive costing controls
Application of costing concepts in the analysis of different areas of costing.
Variance Analysis and reporting
Monitoring and reconciliation of production variances
Month End Closing Activities
Execute other related assignments as directed by HOD
Co-ordinate with the team for smooth implementation of the assignments
This position fits for Those Qualified Students who want to excel in Cost and Management Accounting. This position delivers extensive training of the SAP Management Books which comprises of following Sub Modules;
Cost Element Accounting
Cost Center Accounting
Profit Center Accounting
Internal Order Accounting
Product Cost Controlling
Profitability Analysis
The most appealing thing about this job is the exposure of the students towards Cost and Management Accounting in a world renowned best ERP (SAP) systems.
Required Skills:
Following is the detail of job Requirement and its deliverables;
Having Excellent Communication Skills and Personality
Ability to grasp and communicate complex information and relationships
Strong analytical skills
Resource and Time Management skills
ERP system SAP Controlling module Knowledge (would have an added advantage)
Tools
SAP, Microsoft Word, Microsoft Excel, Microsoft PowerPoint,Microsoft Outlook
Required Skills:
SAP, Microsoft Word, Microsoft Excel, Microsoft PowerPoint, Microsoft Outlook,
LUMS
